I'm a bit late for this little review, but: 

A: It's a bit quiet and cuts of at the last 5 minutes of the movie. 4/10 (given it's a first release)

V: The video is a bit too glare-y and during the big race scene you can't see anything.  It also seems to have been recorded at a weird cropped Resolution. 3/10

As for how steady the video was, You MUST of been using a tripod. I swear, you have the most steady hand in the world. 10/10

Overall: for a First release this upload is pretty damned good. Thank you for it! 17/30 - 56%
